{"tid":1708250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"心灰意冷 有個涼薄的家 比人趕左出街","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T18:34:30.000Z","uid":338603,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c9202b86a5628f62661152a3024f481215639048","tid":1708250,"uid":338603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"老豆老母一直深藍<br />\n紅底極深藍<br />\n都無咩人性 之前話要用真槍殺示威者<br />\n我知同佢地政見唔同一定會嘈 所以約法左三章係屋企唔講政治 咁當然佢當我唱歌啦佢地咪又係照鬧示威者<br />\n前個排班狗周圍拉人周圍殺人<br />\n兩老係群少左屌示威者<br />\n以為佢地都識識地分下是非<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點知</span></span><br />\n今日返到屋企 <br />\n我老母屌9我<br />\n講個藍屍好撚慘比人燒<br />\n我話事出必有因啦 班廢老藍絲周圍斬人殺人你地又扮睇唔到<br />\n佢話一件事還一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲on99嘗試同佢左半粒鐘講道理<br />\n最後一句撻埋黎話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">咁你而加係咪要淋我火水</span></span><br />\n真係喊撚左 <br />\n我喊係因為點解佢地可以咁涼薄咁冷血<br />\n好似係佢地既心中我係個無人性既人<br />\n係咁屌7我無人性無良知<br />\n又叫我去死<br />\n最後比佢趕左出街<br />\n<br />\n想取下暖姐 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好撚辛苦呀！</span><br />\n已有地方落腳"},{"pid":"a66e25ab4ea574231ce6580e8d9fabad9fff97eb","tid":1708250,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b84fcf22b91b25063a95cf58c7527bb7d41b0ec","tid":1708250,"uid":29044,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:57:41.000Z","msg":"加油 人大個始終都要離開父母<br />\n當提早咗啲"},{"pid":"b7d3aa6e87bc7e40504e80f26035044b32abaaad","tid":1708250,"uid":204933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"14893056d53b5768d8251d806743c7918ff4f2db","tid":1708250,"uid":282289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:5